# Example

## `AuthServiceTest.java`

```java
@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)
class AuthServiceTest {

    @InjectMocks
    private AuthService authService;

    @Mock
    private LancelotClient lancelotClient;

    @Mock
    private RedisAuthTransactionService txService;

    @Test
    void shouldStartAuthentication() {

        AppConfigResponse app = new AppConfigResponse();
        app.setClientId("b2boost");
        app.setIssuerUri("http://keycloak/realm");
        app.setRedirectUri("http://callback");

        when(lancelotClient.getApp("B2BOOST_BE")).thenReturn(app);

        String redirect = authService.startAuthentication("B2BOOST_BE");

        assertNotNull(redirect);
        verify(txService).save(any());
    }
}
```

